Day 82: Create Ansible Inventory for App Server Testing

Date: December 16, 2025
Overview
Set up Ansible inventory for managing multiple servers.
Key Concepts Learned

Inventory file structure
Host groups
Variables in inventory
INI vs YAML format

Inventory File
ini[app_servers]
app1 ansible_host=192.168.1.10 ansible_user=admin
app2 ansible_host=192.168.1.11 ansible_user=admin

[db_servers]
db1 ansible_host=192.168.1.20

[all:vars]
ansible_python_interpreter=/usr/bin/python3

Challenges Faced
SSH connection issues and getting host key verification working properly.
